        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "If n = 4, we must have equality in the AM-HM inequality, which only happens when k1 = k2 = k3 = k4 = 4.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5563909790156721,
          0.5682043651241705,
