        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Hence the solutions are n = 1 and k1 = 1, n = 3 and (k1, k2, k3) is a permutation of (2,3,6), and n = 4 and (k1, k2, k3, k4) = (4,4,4,4).",
