        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Since there are n(n - 1) choices for which two points act as li and @2, the probability of at least one acute angle is n(n - 2)2-n+1.",
        "bbox": [
          0.12746288285053298,
